by his many friends so that others may enjoy this place which he found so special
Ste - an amazing son brother
Love always
Mum, Dad, Mike Rich x

Inscription 2)
No other place could be more fitting 
our fondest memories will forever be here
You were an inspiration to all that knew you
exemplifying honesty, trust and friendship
Considered too smooth for us all
Our love always
Your friends
